column5: looking at going to lac seul (CHAMBERLIN NARROWS) EARLY JULY OR EARLY AUGUST...HAVE FISHED IT MANY TIMES IN MAY WITH GREAT LUCK,BUT NEVER ANY LATER...ANY FEEDBACK WOULD BE APPRICIATED...SIZE- QTY-DEPTH YOU WERE FISHING ECT...ALWAYS FISH 10 TO 16 FEET IN THE SPRING...THANKS FOR YOUR FEEDBACK
good question,I have never been there in july or august and hope someone who knows has an answer.
